headline: Solventum to Present Value Creation Formula and Long-Range Plan at 2025 Investor Day
summary: Solventum (NYSE: SOLV) today hosts its 2025 Investor Day and will outline strategic priorities for the Company, its business segments, and its long-range plan (LRP) to drive growth and value creation.
